==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Deca-
<hw>Dec"a-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <pos>pref.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Ten</er>.]</ety> <def>A prefix, from Gr. <grk>de`ka</grk>,
signifying <it>ten</it>;</def> <specif>specifically:</specif>
<fld>(Metric System)</fld>, <def>a prefix signifying the weight or
measure that is <sig>ten times</sig> the principal unit.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Decacerata</ent>⟦br⟧
